{
  "texts": [
    "Many businesses are unaware of the wide range of activities on the dark web, including posting sensitive information that can be exploited for financial gain.",
    "Therefore, keeping confidentiality and preventing negative publicity are significant challenges for businesses.",
    "In addition, it is difficult for companies to track and prevent criminal activities on the dark web because criminals can access it easily and disappear without leaving much trace.It is common for attackers to make their stolen data public, which helps reveal the current state of cybersecurity and potential threats.",
    "According to a surface and dark web dataset study, 71 cyberattacks were generated worldwide, with the US being the top target for state-sponsored hackers [18].",
    "The study proposed the FinFrame framework as a four-step approach to secure financial organizations."
  ]
}